00:32:37,550 --> 00:32:39,280
Keluarga kerajaan itu tidak punya hati.

467
00:32:40,240 --> 00:32:42,840
Setelah diketahui bahwa Selir Virtue
hamil,

468
00:32:43,720 --> 00:32:45,650
Dia diinterogasi setiap malam.

469
00:32:46,310 --> 00:32:48,286
Sampai malam Festival Laba,

470
00:32:48,310 --> 00:32:50,910
ketika Istana Qingyuan
tiba-tiba terbakar...

471
00:32:51,590 --> 00:32:52,047
Tuan Wei? Anda.

472
00:32:52,071 --> 00:32:53,680
Pasukan Garda Kekaisaran sedang berpatroli

473
00:32:53,790 --> 00:32:55,087
bergegas memadamkan api,

474
00:32:55,111 --> 00:32:59,330
[Istana Qingyuan]

475
00:32:56,070 --> 00:32:57,670
Baru kemudian mengetahui bahwa Wei Yan

476
00:32:57,850 --> 00:32:59,976
telah memasuki Ibu Kota tanpa dekrit

477
00:33:00,000 --> 00:33:02,086
dan muncul di Istana Terlarang.

478
00:33:02,110 --> 00:33:02,720
Pergi!

479
00:33:02,920 --> 00:33:04,420
Zhao Xun pernah mengaku

480
00:33:05,480 --> 00:33:08,540
bahwa kebakaran istana itu disebabkan
oleh Putri Mahkota Chengde.

481
00:33:09,200 --> 00:33:11,200
Apakah ada cerita tersembunyi di balik ini?

482
00:33:12,270 --> 00:33:15,790
Pernahkah Anda melihat air dilemparkan ke dalam api?

483
00:33:16,310 --> 00:33:18,170
